{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id902e53e2-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s3224"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3224"},"text":"§ 3224.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reevaluation of nuclear fuel cycle","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The President shall take immediate initiatives to invite all nuclear supplier and recipient nations to reevaluate all aspects of the nuclear fuel cycle, with emphasis on alternatives to an economy based on the separation of pure plutonium or the presence of high enriched uranium, methods to deal with spent fuel storage, and methods to improve the safeguards for existing nuclear technology. The President shall, in the first report required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s3281"},"text":"section 3281 of this title","children":[],"tail":", detail the progress of such international reevaluation."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id902e53e3-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/242/tI/s105"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–242, title I, § 105","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-03-10"},"text":"Mar. 10, 1978","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/92/123"},"text":"92 Stat. 123","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id902e53e4-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id902e53e5-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"id902e53e6-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section effective ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-03-10"},"text":"Mar. 10, 1978","children":[],"tail":", except as otherwise provided and regardless of any requirements for the promulgation of implementing regulations, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/242/s603/c"},"text":"section 603(c) of Pub. L. 95–242","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s3201"},"text":"section 3201 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"id902e53e7-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"delegationOfFunctions","id":"id902e53e8-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Delegation of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Secretary of State responsible for performing functions vested in President under this section, see section 2(a) of Ex. Ord. No. 12058, ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-05-11"},"text":"May 11, 1978","children":[],"tail":", 43 F.R. 20947, set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s3201"},"text":"section 3201 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
